25679227561317327199.Text: Yes. My brother Dalin and I were planning on going in. He, however, would like to wait for more help. Our father perished inside, and we wish to avenge his death. I, however, believe that this is a matter of family honor, and we should go it alone.

292195281322747724.Text: Excellent! My brother Daris and I were just discussing the same thing. Years ago, our father perished in these ruins, may he rest well. We wish to clear the place of the evil that resides inside. I believe that the more who will help us, the better. My brother believes that it is a matter of family honor, and we must do it ourselves.
